2f5a " Ele polghe Kiria quin Sica waicka henes on wehe wica "  Agricola » Julkaisut » Kirja-arvostelut » Caedite eos .
Novit enim Dominus qui sunt eius .
Caedite eos .
Novit enim Dominus qui sunt eius .
16.1.2002 Kari Hintsala  <  karihintsala @ hotmail.com  >  FM ,  Turku O’Shea ,  Stephen :  The Perfect Heresy .
The Revolutionary Life and Death of the Medieval Cathars .
. Profile Books Ltd ,  2001 .
